title: Adobe Photoshop Actions, Lightroom Presets and RAW Presets
description:
Collection of Photoshop Actions, Lightroom and RAW Presets

Some of the most popular stuff from 2008

I compressed the whole directory to avoid broken seeds

I used 7-ZIP to compress (Google-it before bitching about it)

7-ZIP can be opened with WINRAR or WINZIP

I use a PC and don't give a F$#@ about MAC complaints

Most everything is PC & MAC compatible (get a clue before leaving stupid remarks)
